    "body": "There are menu item roles for this `zoomin`, and `zoomout`, and `resetzoom`, http://electron.atom.io/docs/api/menu-item/#new-menuitemoptions\n\nThey were added in `1.3.3`.\n\nYou can also implement custom zooming yourself, you might want to take a look at https://github.com/electron/electron/pull/6677 for more code examples for how to do this.\n"
